Janitor's Closet is not necessarily the culprit here. Some of your mods use a texture file format which KSP 1.8 does not support anymore: 

[ERR 23:37:40.684] DDS: DXT3(256x160, MipMap=True) - DXT3 format is NOT supported. Use DXT5

[WRN 23:37:40.684] Texture load error in 'C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Kerbal Space Program\GameData\AirplanePlus\Agencies\KerbalStandard.dds'

You will need updates for (at least) AirplanePlus, BDArmory and InterstellarFuelSwitch. Check your mods for compatibility with 1.8.
